profile:
Expert Electric - We're your neighborhood's electrician

We provide residential and commercial electrical services to: Vancouver, North and West Vancouver, Burnaby, New Westminster, Richmond, Delta, Coquitlam area, Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Surrey, Langley, White Rock, Abbotsford and Mission.

We've got the power you need! Our trained electricians are the best in the industry, and can repair any issue, guaranteed! From installations to emergencies, big or small... our electricians can perform the job. We focus on the relationship and getting you the things you need to enjoy life!

Why call us first? 

•We are easy to reach - Real people answer our phones, not machines.
•1,000’s of parts on our trucks - For on the spot repairs in your home or business.
•Well Trained Courteous Technicians - we successfully perform repair to thousands of electrical problems every year.
•Up Front Guaranteed Pricing - you know the price before the work begins.
•24 hour emergency service.
•Quick response time
•Trained electricians
•Personalized scheduling

•Ceiling Fan Installation / Maintenance

•Motors

profile: Oxbow Electric is fully committed to providing our customers with the best possible electrical construction experience.  With our core values of reliability, professionalism, integrity, quality and safety we strive for perfection and detail until you are fully satisfied.  We specialize in residential, commercial and industrial services.  Whether you're in need of a small wiring fix, LED upgrades, small or large renovations, service upgrades or brand new builds both residential and commercial we get the job done right.  We are available 7 days a week and serve all of the Okanagan, Osoyoos, Oliver, Ok Falls, Penticton, Summerland, Peachland, West Kelowna and Kelowna.  We also serve Rock Creek, Grand Forks, Keremeos and Princeton.

profile:
Kelteck Electrical Ltd is a full service electrical contracting company dedicated to customer service, safety and craftsmanship; delivering the technical expertise required for modern, efficient and cost effective electrical solutions. Our team members bring years of experience in high end residential home construction, major commercial and data projects, institutional and industrial construction and maintenance. Kelteck creates lasting partnerships based on technical expertise and safe, efficient delivery of professional services. Electrical installations can be simple, intuitive and functional but they can also be messy, difficult to use and very dangerous. We provide our clients with clean, professional installs which instill assuredness that the job has been done right and meets all codes, regulations and safety standards.

Kelteck Electrical Ltd. is a Kelowna based electrical contractor. Owner James Kennedy has a history in high end residential home construction, major commercial and data projects, and industrial construction and maintenence. James has worked in the Okanagan and Kootenays in houses with full integration and control, commercial projects in the Landmark Buildings and Orchard Park Mall and in automation for the fruit industry. He has also been an Electrical and Instrumentation Supervisor in the oil and gas industry in Alberta
